UPDATE talent SET bio = 'Few selectors channel Latin groove and underground minimalism quite like FUMIX. His sets are a masterclass in tension — deep, rolling tech house foundations laced with percussive Latin heat that refuses to let the body stand still. Whether he''s carving through a peak-hour slot or holding down a warm-up with surgical restraint, there''s an unmistakable intentionality to every transition. The result is a sound that feels both rooted and forward-thinking: immersive, textured, and built for rooms that value rhythm over hype. One to watch — and one to dance to.' WHERE alias = 'FUMIX';

UPDATE talent SET bio = 'Sereda operates in the space where emotion meets movement. Drawing from RnB''s intimacy, jazz house''s sophistication, and melodic house''s sweeping arrangements, she crafts sets that feel less like DJ performances and more like cinematic experiences. There''s a rare vulnerability in her track selection — moments of stillness that give way to soaring, euphoric builds. Her ability to hold a room in the palm of her hand, guiding listeners through warmth, melancholy, and release, is what sets her apart. In a scene crowded with energy merchants, Sereda is a storyteller.' WHERE alias = 'SEREDA';

UPDATE talent SET bio = 'MIKEANGELO sits at the crossroads of hip-hop''s raw energy and house music''s relentless pulse — and he makes that intersection feel like the only place worth standing. His sets are a study in dynamics: heavy, sample-driven grooves that nod to golden-era boom-bap one moment, then dissolve into driving tech house rhythms the next. What makes him compelling isn''t just range — it''s intention. Every track is placed with purpose, every transition designed to shift the room''s gravity. He doesn''t just read the dancefloor; he rewrites it in real time. A selector''s selector.' WHERE alias = 'MIKEANGELO';